/* Universal autosuggest for ICD-10 codes and drug names. Hits the backend
   on debounced input ≥2 chars; falls back to the local ICD10 array in
   DEMO_MODE so the offline GitHub Pages demo still has some autocomplete.
   Drugs have no DEMO fallback — the panel just stays empty offline.
   Inputs use comma-separated tokens; textareas use the last word at the cursor. */
